cs.SI, cs.SOC, cs.CYBER, cs.DL, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) is the most likely category as the paper uses social network analysis to explore the patterns of leaders communication on Twitter. 
- cs.SOC (Computational Social Science) is also likely as the paper analyzes social media data to understand political communication among world leaders. 
- cs.CYBER (Cybersecurity and Privacy) is a possible category as the paper may touch upon issues related to cybersecurity and privacy in the context of social media use by government actors. 
- cs.DL (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper may use machine learning techniques to analyze the Twitter data. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is a possible category as the paper may use information retrieval techniques to collect and analyze the Twitter data.
